		<P CLASS="i1 b0 a0 justify">
For <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">ὕψει</SPAN> Groskurd conj. <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">ὄψει</SPAN>, and Meineke so reads.
